{"Id":224,"LanguageCodes":["rw","kin"],"Name":"kin-rmcrwanda","Author":"R. M. C. Rwanda","Language":"Kinyarwanda","Description":"Kinyarwanda","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://www.islamic-invitation.com/","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"Ni iki (abahakanyi b’abakurayishi) babazanyaho"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"Ku nkuru ihambaye (Qur’an n’umunsi w’imperuka)"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"(Iyo nkuru) batavugaho rumwe (hagati y’abayemera n’abayihakana)"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"Oya! Rwose bidatinze bazamenya"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"Oya nanone! Bidatinze bazamenya"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"Ese isi ntitwayigize nk’isaso"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"N’imisozi tukayigira nk’imambo"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"Tukanabarema muri ibitsina byombi (ikigabo n’ikigore)"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"Kandi ibitotsi byanyu twabigize uburyo bw’ikiruhuko"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"N’ijoro turigira nk’umwambaro (binyuze mu mwijima waryo)"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"N’amanywa tuyagira ayo gushakiramo imibereho"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"Tunubaka hejuru yanyu (ibirere) birindwi bikomeye"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"Ndetse n’(izuba) turigira itara rimurika"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"Tunamanura mu bicu amazi menshi yisuka"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"Kugira ngo tuyereshe impeke n’ibimera"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"N’imirima y’ibiti byegeranye"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"Mu by’ukuri, umunsi w’urubanza ufite igihe ntarengwa"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"Umunsi impanda izavuzwa, maze mukaza muri amatsinda"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"N’ikirere kizakingurwa maze gihinduke nk’amarembo"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":20,"Text":"N’imisozi izakurwa mu myanya yayo, imere nk’ibirorirori"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":21,"Text":"Mu by’ukuri, umuriro wa Jahanamu urarekereje"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":22,"Text":"Ni wo garukiro ry’ibyigomeke"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":23,"Text":"Bizawubamo imyaka n’imyaniko"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":24,"Text":"(Ibyo byigomeke) ntibizawusogongereramo ubukonje cyangwa ikinyobwa"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":25,"Text":"Uretse amazi yatuye n’amashyira"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":26,"Text":"(Ibyo bikazaba) ari igihembo gikwiye (ibikorwa bibi bakoraga)"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":27,"Text":"Kuko mu by’ukuri, batajyaga bizera ibarura"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":28,"Text":"Ndetse banahinyuraga amagambo yacu cyane"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":29,"Text":"Kandi byose twarabibaruye mu nyandiko"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":30,"Text":"Ngaho nimusogongere (ingaruka z’ibikorwa byanyu bibi), kandi nta kindi tubongerera usibye ibihano"}]}